Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:00.62,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:120620,120620}Maya has a substitute role in the play "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals" with the help of Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:05.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:125425,125425}However, the co-stars who thought of Maya as a "stage storm…"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:09.66,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:129662,129662}…try to trap her by replacing the new revised script with the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:13.93,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:133933,133933}Maya gets on the stage without knowing her words or the storyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.10,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141141,147105}{\an5\pos(766,710)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,0)}—Episode 17—\NWhere is Mr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:37.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157557,157557}Just watch:\NI will make this play flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168101,168101}But Maya doesn't know that,\Nor even her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161361,161361}This scene is where Chie is overwhelmed by her mortifying feelings…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164798,164798}…and shouts that she would rather run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171738,171738}Himekawa Ayumi doesn't know\Nher words, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174874,174874}She ran out onto the stage\Nwhen it wasn't even her turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178178,178178}Let's see what they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191725,191725}With that lily in your mouth, are you going to entertain me just like your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198231,198231}I just heard that your father has become a traveling entertainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202936,202936}What a shame\Nto the Kaidōji family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:26.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206906,206906}What should I do?\NI can't keep quiet forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210577,210577}Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212312,212312}I want to hear your opinion\Nas Chie Kaidōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:35.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215615,215615}As Chie Kaidōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217984,217984}Just answer my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221287,221287}I will answer\Nto your words as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:45.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225091,225091}Ayumi is telling me to proceed\Nwith this scene with all ad-lib.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230030,230030}Do you understand, Chie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232565,232565}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:55.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235101,235101}She accepted the challenge.\NWhat a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:57.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237270,237270}I'll just follow Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239706,239706}I wonder, do you remember when you first came to this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:06.24,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:246246,246246}Ayumi told Maya Chie's situation in her own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:09.21,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:249215,249215}Chie was born to Yukihiro, the fifth son of Kaidōji, and a geisha from Fukagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:14.82,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:254821,254821}Yukihiro has returned with Chie once,\Nbut he left her to be with another geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261194,261194}Everyone used to mistake you as a maid,\Nbecause you were always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:26.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266599,266599}Ayumi, do you want to\Nmake me sad or mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273239,273239}What do you think about this flier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279212,279212}What a great father, to have his\Npicture on something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:43.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283416,283416}I see, she's trying\Nto make me upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286619,286619}What a great father he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289956,289956}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292592,292592}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:54.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294160,294160}That's it.\NNow we're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296863,296863}What nonsense!\NAre you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:04:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299466,299466}He dishonored the Kaidōji family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302702,302702}What about the Kaidōji family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304671,304671}All they did was to try and make my loving father and mother separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308541,308541}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309809,309809}What an ungrateful thing to say after all they have done for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313880,313880}No! The Kaidōji family, who influences things with its power and money, I hate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323623,323623}Such brave actresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325592,325592}They match each other's emotions and words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328695,328695}Besides, they are almost\Nfollowing the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331431,331431}All they have to do now is to get Chie to run off the stage saying she would run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335502,335502}Is that right? Then, why don't you run away, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340373,340373}You and your father are a stain on our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343576,343576}Everyone has to live unpleasantly because of that stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346713,346713}Why don't you go to that geisha mother of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349082,349082}Or go after your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:05:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359325,359325}He's a poor actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361828,361828}Why don't you go with the poor actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364698,364698}I hate this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:09.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369336,369336}I want to say that I want to leave this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:12.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372205,372205}But what if that's not in the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:14.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374307,374307}I'll make a terrible mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395995,395995}This… This house…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398331,398331}I'll… I'll go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401134,401134}She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402769,402769}I never want to see your face again, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405171,405171}Go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:46.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406773,406773}Get off the stage from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417884,417884}Excellent job.\NYou did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420453,420453}Uh, my last words,\Nwas that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423990,423990}Okay? Without these words,\Nthe play couldn't have gone on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428595,428595}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430196,430196}Chie's running away triggers the breakdown of the Kaidōji family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435235,435235}It was that important…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:17.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437971,437971}I might not have said those words\Nif Ayumi didn't hit me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442175,442175}What, Chie is leaving the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:27.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447113,447113}Ayumi, what a talented person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463530,463530}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465465,465465}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467334,467334}We wouldn't have known what to do if you didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470970,470970}Then you should learn from this and never do a stupid thing like switching a script again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478078,478078}She knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483616,483616}Ayumi, thank you so—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485251,485251}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:09.62,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:489622,489622}Backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:11.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491658,491658}Ayumi, she completely brought me into her pace and made me say the needed words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:17.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497864,497864}I can't win.\NI can't beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:22.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502836,502836}Kitajima Maya. She used her full body to sense where I as going, and followed me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:29.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509442,509442}She was as good as I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:32.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512045,512045}No, I knew the storyline of the fourth act, so I had the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:37.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517317,517317}She still did as good as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:43.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523823,523823}I lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:49.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529496,529496}Ayumi, a person\Nwith such a great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533099,533099}Mr. Himekawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536102,536102}Director!\NAyumi did great on stage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:02.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542976,542976}Her father is a movie director\Nand her mother a well-known actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:06.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546579,546579}She has a shining beauty\Nand a genius of a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550216,550216}Compared to her,\Nhow boring am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554721,554721}What's wrong, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556623,556623}You seem down despite\Nyour great success tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559359,559359}Ayumi saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562562,562562}It wasn't my work,\Nbut Ayumi's talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565465,565465}Let me take you home.\NIt's pouring outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568435,568435}No, thank you!\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571471,571471}You still hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574407,574407}Yes, I hate you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576576,576576}Aren't you glad that things\Nare going your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579879,579879}You should be satisfied when you have the play rights for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588755,588755}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591891,591891}I get what I want\Nusing any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595462,595462}I don't give a damn\Nwhat happens to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598998,598998}Are you happy to hear me\Nsay that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603470,603470}How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:05.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605238,605238}Such a terrible person.\NAs cold-blooded as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:15.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615081,615081}I won't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:17.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617717,617717}I will never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:26.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626092,626092}I wonder if Maya is looking\Nfor her mom in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632432,632432}Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634701,634701}You're soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:36.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636803,636803}I can't become "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640874,640874}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641941,641941}Even if I run as hard as I can,\NI can never catch up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652085,652085}Mr. Masumi, what have you been\Nthinking about all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655922,655922}Could I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656823,656823}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659225,659225}The girl who ran from you,\NKitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665265,665265}I must be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666866,666866}She was wonderful today,\Ndespite what all happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671271,671271}You almost lost yourself then,\Nunlike your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676409,676409}I was just worried that\Nshe would ruin the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679879,679879}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681581,681581}What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684184,684184}I'll take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688088,688088}Yes, that was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:30.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690290,690290}That was all…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:35.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695628,695628}I feel drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:39.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699232,699232}I can't find my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:41.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701434,701434}I can't even practice acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:45.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705672,705672}Sakurakōji didn't come to "The Smile of Stone" at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:51.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711945,711945}How lonely.\NEveryone's gone all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717217,717217}Maya, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720453,720453}It's him!\NLook at the presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723223,723223}Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725258,725258}It's like a sugar daddy\Nwith all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:10.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730296,730296}"I saw your act in 《The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals》."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:12.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732999,732999}"I was impressed with your act as Chie,\Neven as a substitute."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:17.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737370,737370}"I'm looking forward to seeing you\Non stage again soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:20.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740974,740974}You were there again for me,\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:27.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747414,747414}I still have someone on my side.\NMr. Purple Rose.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:33.71,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:753711,753711}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:37.50,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:757507,757507}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:40.46,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:760468,760468}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:40.89,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:760894,760894}Maya enrolled in Hitotsubashi High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:44.76,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:764764,764764}It is also known as the "talent school," and there are many actors and actresses in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.07,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:771071,771071}There is also an acting club known for its elite members who have passed challenging acting tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:12:58.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778878,778878}I wonder what they are like, winning the "All-Japan Acting Contest" every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784718,784718}The demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784851,784851}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787253,787253}Hide the babies,\Nhide the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787854,787854}Look, that's Kanaya Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789956,789956}The best actress of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:11.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791224,791224}Kanaya Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797664,797664}The demon!\NIt's here, the baby eater is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803236,803236}Where are the children!?\NWhere are the kids!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806306,806306}If not them,\NI'll eat you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808975,808975}Go away, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:36.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816049,816049}"The scene, played as an ad-lib\Nby Kitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi…"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:38.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818752,818752}"…was an unexpected plus\Nfor the night's play."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:39.11,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:819119,819119}The Cherry Tree\Nof Dream Festivals
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:42.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822522,822522}"Much is expected from their\Ncompetitive yet equal talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830930,830930}Their competitive yet equal talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:02.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842809,842809}What talent…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844611,844611}Are you Ms. Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846880,846880}Uhm, yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849115,849115}This was left at the reception desk\Nwith your name and class on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853219,853219}Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856322,856322}Oh, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857857,857857}Sorry, I'll get it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:19.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859826,859826}Please wait for me.\NDon't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:25.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865065,865065}Where is he?\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867067,867067}What a nice car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877677,877677}A purple rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880547,880547}Whose car is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882349,882349}Hayami Masumi.\NFrom Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884617,884617}Hayami Masumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886586,886586}He just went into\Nthe Principal's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888555,888555}He's a great businessman, I hear\Nhe donates lots of money every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:55.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895528,895528}A purple rose in the car of\NMetropolitan Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:57.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897831,897831}Perhaps Mr. Purple Rose\Nwas in this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:05.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905839,905839}And he might be in the\NPrincipal's office with Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:11.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911644,911644}He must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914381,914381}H-Hey, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916750,916750}Sorry, but I need to see the Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918418,918418}He has a guest right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924391,924391}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925592,925592}Yes. I'm Kitajima Maya\Nfrom Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928795,928795}Well, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931164,931164}Hell, little girl.\NDid you come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934401,934401}No! I'm looking for\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939039,939039}Hmph.\NMr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941441,941441}I saw a purple rose in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944477,944477}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947547,947547}You know him.\NYou know Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950150,950150}Please tell me who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952786,952786}All I want to do is tell him how much I appreciate him… for all he does for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960760,960760}How much he encourages me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965565,965565}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967667,967667}Oh, I just remembered who had the purple rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971171,971171}I picked up an actress on the way here,\Nand she had some flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976142,976142}An actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979145,979145}She had some flowers with purple roses in it, so she must be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981481,981481}Sorry it's not who\Nyou were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985352,985352}I thought I could finally thank him…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988988,988988}He knows how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997997,997997}Please shut the door\Nwhen you are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001468,1001468}Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:54.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014981,1014981}"May your school life be filled\Nwith joy and achievement."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021121,1021121}I want to see you,\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:04.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024424,1024424}I wonder what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032332,1032332}Hey, welcome home.\NHow was school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035235,1035235}Look at this!\NIt's Mr. Purple Rose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037937,1037937}He came to your school?\NWhew, what a love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040640,1040640}Stop it, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045378,1045378}I wonder when I can go\Non stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048481,1048481}I want Mr. Purple Rose\Nto see me on stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051785,1051785}Teacher didn't order you off the stage out of hate, and she'll get you back on there again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057190,1057190}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059225,1059225}Why don't you come and see our practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065365,1065365}Are you Ms. Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066433,1066433}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067801,1067801}This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070470,1070470}Hasegawa,\NMetropolitan Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073073,1073073}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079179,1079179}The role of Helen Keller?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081247,1081247}Yes. Well, we have a total\Nof five candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084751,1084751}We'll have an audition in August\Nto make our final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088888,1088888}Audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091658,1091658}Helen Keller has a triple disability\Nand acts like a wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096262,1096262}It will be a tough role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098431,1098431}Who are the other candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101334,1101334}Shiratori Reina,\NHayakawa Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103870,1103870}She's an upcoming actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105739,1105739}Kanaya Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107340,1107340}Kanaya Emi?\NFrom Hitotsubashi High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111678,1111678}Yes.\NShe's full of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114280,1114280}So, who is the fourth one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116116,1116116}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117350,1117350}Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119152,1119152}Let me also mention that\Nthe director will be Onedera Hajime…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124124,1124124}…and the main role, Annie Sullivan,\Nwill be played by Himekawa Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127861,1127861}Ha!\NThat's a fair competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131664,1131664}It's like Maya going\Ninto enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135435,1135435}Please don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137570,1137570}Our audition is very fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140340,1140340}The fact that Himekawa Ayumi is the daughter of the main role won't affect it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144944,1144944}Then I guess that's okay.\NHuh, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147814,1147814}Thank you for the offer,\Nbut I would like to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151317,1151317}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152052,1152052}I would like to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155055,1155055}Maya, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158391,1158391}This role sure will be hard, but it's\Nalso a rewarding challenge for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160960,1160960}You will grow as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163329,1163329}I know you have harsh feelings towards Metropolitan Entertainment, but this is a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167500,1167500}You have to grab your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170270,1170270}Well, please take your time\Nto think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173340,1173340}I won't take the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175475,1175475}Please change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181915,1181915}What's wrong?\NIt's not like you, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184150,1184150}I can't win.\NI can't win against Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186052,1186052}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200000,1200000}You really are going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201701,1201701}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202302,1202302}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203803,1203803}I will be at the mansion in Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206172,1206172}Practice hard. I'll talk to your grandmother every three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210076,1210076}The next time I see you, it will be at the audition, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213613,1213613}Yes. Until then, we won't be mother and daughter anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218618,1218618}Yes. I want to get the role with my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221821,1221821}I will choose Helen fairly from an actress' point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228194,1228194}Good bye now, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231064,1231064}Good bye, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238972,1238972}I heard you declined the audition for Helen's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240874,1240874}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241274,1241274}You are afraid of Ayumi,\Nis that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244377,1244377}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246379,1246379}You got scared after being lead by Ayumi in "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251851,1251851}Maya, you are hereby expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254421,1254421}Expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255955,1255955}You knew you weren't allowed to get on stage, yet you took the role in "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260160,1260160}That's reason enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262429,1262429}Expelled…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264964,1264964}But, if you win the role of Helen,\Nthen I'll reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269169,1269169}Helen's role?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270570,1270570}If not, you can not only forget about practicing at my school, but "The Crimson Goddess" as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:18.77,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1278778,1278778}Metropolitan Entertainment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283717,1283717}You're still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285919,1285919}It's my way of taking a break\Nto read the proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289222,1289222}Sounds like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292092,1292092}About "The Miracle Worker," we'll have the interview next month, and the audition is for August 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298732,1298732}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301267,1301267}So, I see that you haven't heard if Kitajima Maya will be at the audition or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305605,1305605}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307173,1307173}Don't worry. She replied and she will be at the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313113,1313113}Maybe you should send some purple roses to encourage her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:05.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325925,1325925}Maya, you are hereby expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:10.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330296,1330296}But, if you win the role of Helen,\Nthen I'll reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:19.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339572,1339572}I will play the disabled Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:21.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341508,1341508}Acting is all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:28.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348448,1348448}Go for it, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:30.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350150,1350150}If you can play Helen, then you will be one step closer to "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:39.05,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1359059,1359059}To continue with acting as her future, she has to win the role of Helen Keller, Maya told herself.
